B.Mw=new A.K(B.A,"Tense Backshift Rule",'When the reporting verb is **past** (said, told, reported), tenses shift back:\n\n| Direct | Reported |\n|---|---|\n| is/am/are | **was/were** |\n| was/were | **had been** |\n| will | **would** |\n| can | **could** |\n| must | **had to** |\n| has/have + V3 | **had** + V3 |\n\n"The system **is** malfunctioning." \u2192\nThe pilot said the system **was** malfunctioning.',null,null,null)
